og:description: OneKey® MLS has acquired Mid-Hudson MLS, a privately, broker-owned multiple listing service with more than 1,400 agents and approximately 350 offices throughout Dutchess County and the Mid-Hudson Valley area. The acquisition brings OneKey MLS’s subscriber base to nearly 50,000 real estate professionals in more than 4,800 participating offices, serving Montauk to Manhattan and north through the Hudson Valley.
